  <summary>2/3/1999--Introduced.
Declares that: (1) the President should seek a public renunciation by the People's Republic of China of any use of force, or threat to use force, against Taiwan; and (2) the United States should help Taiwan defend itself in case of threats or a military attack by China.</summary>
